      "description": "This pristine E92 M3 represents a superlative example of the S65-powered era. The 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS, delivering linear power to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator service. The chassis integrity is absolute, complemented by a weight-reducing carbon fiber roof and Electronic Damper Control. Finished in its original factory coat with zero imperfections, this vehicle offers a turn-key experience for the purist seeking high-revving atmospheric performance.",
